short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Copy grades from Google Classroom to Arkansas eSchool Teacher Access Center

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension allows you to copy grades from Google Classroom Gradebook to the eSchool Teacher Access Center Gradebook. You can quickly copy an entire column of grades for a specific assignment.
